  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith meets Julie",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa has assured the US Ambassador to Sri Lanka, Julie Sang, that they will provide full cooperation to the government in the common programs to recover the country from crisis conditions.",
        "He also pointed out that this government is over-indulging in unnecessary arrests, attacks and repression.",
        "The American Ambassador to Sri Lanka, Julie Sung, met and discussed with the Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa yesterday (19).",
        "Special attention was paid to the crisis situation Sri Lanka is currently facing and the political situation, and joint activities to obtain international cooperation were also discussed.",
        "The leader of the opposition party has said that he is ready to provide the complete support of the opposition to get the cooperation of international countries and to get the cooperation of other financial aid organizations including the International Monetary Fund.",
        "Also, this government is over-indulging in unnecessary arrests, attacks and repression. It is not a healthy city. The Leader of the Opposition pointed out that we are not going to accept this as an opposition party.",
        "Emphasizing that he will never accept violations of human rights and suppression of democracy, the ambassador also said how all sectors of Sri Lanka must work together to address the urgent and long-term needs of the Sri Lankan people."
      ],
